name: Game Color and Light
description: Shiraz is a city that with its unique attractions can provide a memorable travel experience. One of the most important and beautiful attractions of this lovely city is Nasir Al-Molk Mosque. No one has seen a mosque with colorful windows. Nasir Al-Molk Mosque in Shiraz is one of the oldest mosques in the city and attracts many tourists every year. One of the first and best descriptions that can be said about this mosque is the play of color and light; Since the combination of the two is always amazing, the best possible title for Nasir Al-Molk Mosque in Shiraz is a place to play with color and light.
